ombination of technical reliability, stress handling, and responsibility, with no deficits in decision\u2011making or situational awareness. Given the available evidence, Candidate\u202fB appears the most balanced fit for the long\u2011distance pilot role.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_2\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
