ssessment, computer proficiency, stress handling) and a high level of conscientiousness, which directly support safe, long\u2011haul operations. While his interpersonal issues are notable, they are comparable in severity to the interpersonal deficits of the other candidates (A\u2019s show\u2011off attitude, C\u2019s egocentricity and communication difficulty, D\u2019s arrogance and hot temper) and do not outweigh his technical advantages. Therefore, Candidate\u202fB remains the most balanced and suitable choice for the long\u2011distance pilot role.\nMETADATA_JSON:\n{\"agent\": \"agent_1\", \"vote\": \"Candidate B\"}"}
